#### Disestablishment

In mid-2000, CTF 77 was officially disestablished as a distinct task force within the 7th Fleet. Its responsibilities were absorbed by CTF 70, Commander, Battle Force, U.S. 7th Fleet. The Commander, Task Force 70, continues to be dual-hatted as the Commander, [Carrier Strike Group Five](/Carrier_Strike_Group_Five). The staff for this command is homeported at [United States Fleet Activities Yokosuka, Japan](/United_States_Fleet_Activities_Yokosuka) when not embarked aboard the aircraft carrier also homeported there, currently the USS *Ronald Reagan*.